h3. Summary
JIRA Cloud's Backup Manager just hangs at the _Starting_ process and never completes. No error message is displayed in the screen.

h3. Steps to Reproduce
# Have a JIRA Cloud with a huge amount of attachments files (at least more than 5GB)
# Generate a backup with the additional files checkbox checked

h3. Expected Results
After a certain time the backup is generated and the link to download it is presented.
Or an error message appears in the screen if it fails in the background.
